text:
Hey all,

Happy Friday!! Any arts and craft people here?

Thinking about hosting a card making day next weekend (Nov 5) if anybody is down…Saturday?? 2pm-6pm?? :lower_left_paintbrush:

I’m thinking about making Christmas cards…. but obviously you can make any card! Or if you want a customized card made for your family, friends or significant other (for this year or next), tell me… really! I’m pretty creative, or bad. It’s a gamble but you have nothing to lose :woman-shrugging::skin-tone-2:

PS I see a lot of people have started filling out the survey for my research project. Thank you much!! It will help when I get to share the results with Joyner, and new chapters are opened!! :pleading_face::heart:

Cherie Lum
